Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:17.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}an Error code Error code Error code No Error
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:26.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即便我們選擇的未來不是正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:33.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}只要你我的心意相同足矣
